> Usage
To run the command line prompt
$ ruby prompt.rb
then input the data block

> Website
You can see this repo in action at http://luhnvalidation.herokuapp.com

> Test
Run the credit_card_spec.rb for automated testing
$ spec credit_card_spec.rb

